English: It was really cool and it was cool to really get off campus a little bit
meaning outside of the estate in Puerto Vallarta
and see like how real people were living there.
Chinese: 这真的很酷，真正离开校园一点点也很酷
意思是在波多黎各瓦拉塔的庄园外
并看看那里真实人们的生活方式。
